sparql_query_kg2:
 Given the context and the specific information provided, here is the SPARQL query for Knowledge Graph 2 (OpenAlex) to find the average number of co-authors for papers published by E. G. Omodeo:

```sparql
PREFIX oa: <https://semopenalex.org/ontology/>
SELECT (AVG(?count) AS ?answer) {
  SELECT (COUNT(?author) AS ?count) WHERE {
    ?work oa:hasAuthorship ?authorship .
    ?authorship oa:hasAuthor ?author .
    ?author <https://dbpedia.org/ontology/orcidId> "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3917-1942" .
  } GROUP BY ?work
}
```

This query first counts the number of co-authors for each work authored by E. G. Omodeo and then calculates the average of these counts.

