OpenAlex: PREFIX oa: <https://semopenalex.org/ontology/> PREFIX fabio: <http://purl.org/spar/fabio/>  SELECT DISTINCT ?work WHERE { ?work oa:hasAuthorship ?authorship . ?authorship oa:hasAuthor ?author . ?author <https://dbpedia.org/ontology/orcidId> "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5758-1876" .  ?work fabio:hasPublicationYear ?year .  FILTER(?year > YEAR(NOW()) - 5) } 

Example 2: Q: Find the papers written by Ricardo da Silva Torres and Leonor Patricia C. Morellato together.
DBLP: SELECT DISTINCT ?answer WHERE { ?answer <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#authoredBy> <https://dblp.org/pid/s/RicardodaSilvaTorres> . ?answer <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#authoredBy> <https://dblp.org/pid/124/2103> }
OpenAlex: PREFIX oa: <https://semopenalex.org/ontology/>  SELECT DISTINCT ?work WHERE { ?work oa:hasAuthorship ?authorship1 . ?authorship1 oa:hasAuthor ?author1 . ?author1 <https://dbpedia.org/ontology/orcidId> "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9772-263X" .  ?work oa:hasAuthorship ?authorship2 . ?authorship2 oa:hasAuthor ?author2 . ?author2 <https://dbpedia.org/ontology/orcidId> "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5265-8988" .  FILTER(?author1 != ?author2) } 

Example 3: Q: Which publications did Nicholas D. Lane author?
DBLP: SELECT DISTINCT ?answer WHERE { ?answer <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#authoredBy> <https://dblp.org/pid/03/2663> }
OpenAlex: PREFIX oa: <https://semopenalex.org/ontology/>  SELECT DISTINCT ?work WHERE { ?work oa:hasAuthorship ?authorship . ?authorship oa:hasAuthor ?author . ?author <https://dbpedia.org/ontology/orcidId> "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2728-8273" . }  

Example 4: Q: In which venues did Sharma, Deepak publish papers and what are the titles of these papers?
DBLP: SELECT DISTINCT ?firstanswer ?secondanswer WHERE { ?x <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#authoredBy> <https://dblp.org/pid/87/4567-1> . ?x <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#publishedIn> ?firstanswer . ?x <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#title> ?secondanswer }
OpenAlex: PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX oa: <https://semopenalex.org/ontology/>  SELECT DISTINCT ?venue ?title WHERE { ?work oa:hasAuthorship ?authorship . ?authorship oa:hasAuthor ?author . ?author <https://dbpedia.org/ontology/orcidId> "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-8939-9833" .  ?work oa:hasLocation ?location . ?location oa:hasSource ?venue .  ?work dct:title ?title . }
